(require-python '[numpy :as np]
                '[numpy.random :as np.random]
                'matplotlib.pyplot
                '[seaborn :as sns]
                'json)
:ok
(def sine-data
  (-> {:x (range 0 (* 3 np/pi) 0.1)}
      tc/dataset
      (tc/add-column :y #(fun/sin (:x %)))))
